data.name: txtImdbWebUsername.ToolTip
data.value:
Your IMDb User ID starts with 'ur', you can get this from the IMDb website from the address bar when in your profile.
This option only works for profiles marked as 'Public'. Private profiles should use CSV option.

data.name: chkCheckMoviesAddWatchedToWatchlist.ToolTip
data.value: The trakt watchlist contains movies you *want* to watch, once you watch these movies, they are automatically removed. Enable this setting only if you want to insert your watched movies from iCheckMovies into your watchlist, otherwise only movies marked as *watchlist* will be added to your watchlist (recommended).
